extendedInfo.description: Welcome to Maple Street Grill and Uncorked in picturesque Murfreesboro, Tennessee. Come see what everyone is raving about, from fresh seafood to steaks cooked to perfection. Here are some of the features available to you in our application:Keep up-to-date with news and eventsCall us directly from the appView our Menu and SpecialsKeep up to date on new specials arriving dailyGet directions to our storeFind our hours of operationTip calculatorMonthly cooking tips from our Kitchen ManagerDaily Dinner and Wine SpecialsMake reservations and read reviewsCome for the food, stay for the hospitality!
